IN RE: Nomination Petition of Rob BOWERS as Candidate for Member of Dem Executive Committee Ward 36 Division 4 Petition of: Rob Bowers No. 154 EAL 2018 Supreme Court of Pennsylvania. April 19, 2018

ORDER

PER CURIAM .
